00:13:16.733 --> 00:13:20.133
the useful energy and
has categorized

00:13:20.133 --> 00:13:21.500
them here in the green.

00:13:21.500 --> 00:13:27.033
So you can read this by sources,
by use, and by this

00:13:27.033 --> 00:13:34.000
last category of waste
or useful work.

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:35.667
Questions there?

