And we are a high user.

00:15:28.433 --> 00:15:30.933
But there are higher users.

00:15:33.633 --> 00:15:36.567
Why would Iceland, Norway,
Finland, and Canada

00:15:36.567 --> 00:15:38.933
use more than we?

